So was his angle, the shareholders should take the $175 and run? 		  Remember, we wrote it from the selfish standpoint of the Time CEO. Seeing as our recommendation in the memo was counter to everything our beloved professor supported, it will be interesting to see how he grades us on this one. ********************************************** Mark D. Guinney, CFA Consultant Watson Wyatt Investment Consulting 345 California Street, Ste. 1400 San Francisco, CA  94104 (415) 733-4487 ph. (415) 733-4190 fax